# Full-Stack MVP Project - Task Checklist

## Frontend Tasks
- [x] Initialize frontend Vite React TypeScript project and install all dependencies
- [x] Configure TailwindCSS, TypeScript, and project structure (folders: pages, components, context, api, types, i18n)
- [x] Set up i18next with en/ar translations, create translation JSON files for all UI text
- [x] Create shared TypeScript types in src/types/api.ts for API responses and DTOs
- [x] Implement AuthContext with login(), logout(), refreshToken() methods and JWT token storage
- [x] Create Axios instance with request/response interceptors for auto token attachment and refresh
- [x] Create ProtectedRoute component for route protection
- [x] Implement all pages: Landing, Register, Login, Dashboard with forms, validation, and i18n

## Backend Tasks
- [x] Initialize NestJS project and install all dependencies (JWT, Passport, Prisma, bcrypt)
- [x] Create Prisma schema with User model, Role enum, and database configuration
- [x] Create Prisma module and service for database access
- [x] Create auth DTOs (RegisterDto, LoginDto, RefreshTokenDto) with class-validator decorators
- [x] Implement auth service with register (bcrypt), login (JWT generation), and refresh token logic
- [x] Create auth controller with /register, /login, /refresh, /me endpoints
- [x] Implement JWTAuthGuard for JWT authentication
- [x] Implement RolesGuard and @Roles decorator for role-based authorization
- [x] Create user module with admin-only protected route example
- [x] Set up environment variables, JWT configuration, and database connection

## Documentation Tasks
- [x] Create README.md with installation, database setup, and running instructions for both frontend and backend
- [x] Create ToDo file with all tasks listed

